T1  - Long-term outcomes of switching to gonadotrophins versus continuing with clomiphene citrate, with or without intrauterine insemination, in women with normogonadotropic anovulation and clomiphene failure: follow-up study of a factorial randomized clinical trial
A1  - Nahuis M.
A1  - Mol B.W.
A1  - Weiss N.S.
A1  - Bordewijk E.M.
A1  - Jannink T.I.
