AN  - 2025451645
ID  - 37715279 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=37715279]
T1  - SPIOMET4HEALTH-efficacy, tolerability and safety of lifestyle intervention plus a fixed dose combination of spironolactone, pioglitazone and metformin (SPIOMET) for adolescent girls and young women with polycystic ovary syndrome: study protocol for a multicentre, randomised, double-blind, placebo-controlled, four-arm, parallel-group, phase II clinical trial
A1  - Garcia-Beltran C.
A1  - Malpique R.
A1  - Andersen M.S.
A1  - Bas F.
A1  - Bassols J.
A1  - Darendeliler F.
