T1  - Metformin-Fish Oil Adjunct Therapy Improves apoBRemnant Lipoprotein and Triglyceride Levels in Women with Polycystic Ovary Syndrome
T3  - Annual Meeting of the Endocrine Society, ENDO 2020. San Francisco, CA United States.
A1  - Proctor E.
