270. 
TY  - JOUR
DB  - Embase
AN  - 638854459
T1  - Discriminatory value of steroid hormones on polycystic ovary syndrome in women with infertility and obesity
T3  - 38th Hybrid Annual Meeting of the European Society of Human Reproduction and Embryology. Milan Italy.
A1  - Wang Z.
A1  - Van Der Veen A.
A1  - Groen H.
A1  - Cantineau A.E.P.
A1  - Van Oers A.
