ID  - 30612112 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=30612112]
T1  - Acupuncture or metformin to improve insulin resistance in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: Study protocol of a combined multinational cross sectional case-control study and a randomised controlled trial
A1  - Stener-Victorin E.
A1  - Li R.
A1  - Friden C.
A1  - Li D.
A1  - Wang W.
A1  - Wang H.
A1  - Chang C.
