T1  - Metformin treatment before and during IVF or ICSI in PCOS women with BMI < 28 kg/m?: A prospective, randomized, double-blind, multicenter study
T3  - 26th Annual Meeting of the European Society of Human Reproduction and Embryology, ESHRE. Rome Italy.
T3  - (var.pagings).
A1  - Kjotrod S.
